</div>    </div>   </div>  </span> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.pg-get-pid-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <span>   <ul class="simplelist">    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link pg_get_notify()} - 获取 SQL NOTIFY 消息</span></li>   </ul>  </span> </div></div>
